02-Governance-and-Compliance/Acceptable-Use-Policy.md

# Acceptable Use Policy

## Purpose
To define acceptable usage of organizational IT assets.

## Scope
Applies to all employees, contractors, and vendors.

## Policy
- Do not use company assets for illegal activities.
- Do not install unauthorized software.
- Do not share passwords.

## Enforcement
Violations may result in disciplinary action, including termination.

## Review Date
Reviewed annually by the security team.
